text: Santa Maria Coghinas (Cuzìna) is a town and comune in the Province of Sassari in Sardinia, Italy. As of 2016, 1,389 people lived there. Its area is 22.97 km².Istituto nazionale di statistica - Superficie territoriale per zona altimetrica It is 21 meters above sea level. == References == == Other websites == Category:Communes of the Province of Sassari
